==Accolades==
{{BLP sources section|date=September 2016}}
* 1999&amp;nbsp;– Won [[British Comedy Award]], Best Male Comedy Newcomer for ''The 11&amp;nbsp;O'Clock Show''&lt;ref&gt;[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/571351.stm Royles clean up at comedy awards] BBC News. Retrieved 27 February 2012&lt;/ref&gt;
